title: A KCET-related question:
content: i got 95% in my PCM, and if i get 135/180 in KCET, what rank do you think i might get?

comments.body: bro i checked, most websites dont even give anything close to the real results so im asking y'all

I had the exact same score and I got around 2k

Ps: back in 2019â€¦
You'll get somewhere around 3k, give or take 200

You can expect your rank to be within 3k... last yr with this marks my friend got 1.3k rank.. 

and congrats!!

see no website will give you a proper detailed info.. check simplified minds video.. he might give you a vague clarity of how others have performed, depending on that you can assume how safe you are.

No one can predict rank with just the marks, other factors too play an important role in deciding the rank, like the difficulty of kcet and the board ppr, amount of grace marks awarded.
